Intro:
=======
Terrorists have been been keeping Hostages against their will, along with stolen money and goods within a warehouse.
They have also constructed a network of tunnels and a bunker under the grounds.

Terrorists: Your base of operations has been compromised, a local Counter-Terror unit has been dispatched
to neutralize your team and rescue the Hostages! Stop them at all costs!

Counter-Terrorists: Intel has found the locations of a warehouse containing thousands in stolen money and goods, 
along with four captives. Your Mission: Eliminate the Terrorist threat and rescue the Hostages.

Tips:
======
Terrorists: Your spread out at first, so try to regroup, also, if you are overrun, you can retreat to the bunker. 
In the bunker, you can lock down the doors using one of the buttons in the control room, but don't let down your guard...

Counter-Terrorists: The Terrorists are spread out, so try to take them out in the pockets, but be careful that 
they don't surprise you. Also, there are also many routes to take, so be sure to learn them, such as, 
there are more ways into the bunker than just the doors...

Footnote:
=========
There are some glitches, but its my first really good map, but try to have fun!
